Variant in the KY outbreak has 3 key mutations: 

* #D614G = increased transmissibility

* #E484K = in spike protein receptor-binding domain also in B.1.351 (South Africa) and P.1 (Brazil)

* #W152L = might reduce effectiveness of neutralizing antibodies
